snippet.textDisplay: Wow, great strategy, Coke Studio! With the Magical Journey coming out first, on top of everything else that says "Coke Studio Pakistan is the best for..." (musical arrangements, sound, video, story, costumes, sets, ... you name it!), we can now add "Marketing strategy" to the list!! Waah... Xulfi... the greatest entertainment mastermind! (And by the way, thanks for adding "Pakistan" to the Coke Studio name this season). What a collaboration this will turn out to be.... a beloved Balochi singer that I see, half Egyptian/half Norwegian, Indian Norwegian, Irani Norwegian, with QuickStyle we have every kind of Norwegian, and Pakistani at every level! Can't wait... thank you CSP! A big fan from Chicago!
